com.interpss.dstab.mach

Interface Machine

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DynamicDevice, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDynamicSimulation, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DynamicMachine, EConstMachine, Eq1Ed1Machine, Eq1Machine, RoundRotorMachine, SalientPoleMachine
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicMachineImpl, EConstMachineImpl, Eq1Ed1MachineImpl, Eq1MachineImpl, MachineImpl, RoundRotorMachineImpl, SalientPoleMachineImpl

    public interface Machine
extends DynamicDevice
    A representation of the model object 'Machine Adapter'. Machine object adapter to adapt the generic MachineData object to a type specific object. It is a DynamicBusDevice with dynamic behavior implemented. Also it has a list of machine controllers for Exc, Gov and PSS model.

    The following features are supported:

    • Mach Type
    • Speed
    • Angle
    • Efd
    • Pm
    • Pe
    • QGen
    • FG
    • Parent Gen
    • Mach Data
    • Controller List
    • Pe Neg Seq
    See Also:
    DstabMachPackage.getMachine()
